# Inova Finance AI — Project Rules

## Stack

- Monorepo Turborepo + pnpm workspaces
- Next.js 15 App Router (`apps/web`)
- Cloudflare Workers (`workers/app-api`, `workers/messaging`, `workers/agents-runtime`, `workers/embedded-runtime`)
- Prisma + PostgreSQL via Hyperdrive (`packages/db`)
- FastAPI VPS services (`services/ocr`, `services/fiscal`, `services/reporting`)

## Mandatory Headers

Every API request and event MUST include:

- `X-Tenant-Id`
- `X-Branch-Id` (when applicable)
- `X-Correlation-Id`

## Spec Kit

Follow SDD workflow in `.specify/`. Read constitution before implementing features.

## Frontend Checkpoint

Do NOT implement visual layout beyond technical shell until `LAYOUT-APPROVAL-REQUIRED` checkpoint is cleared with the user.

## Language

User-facing strings and specs in pt-BR. Code identifiers in English.
